## 2. API Endpoints (Draft)

**Auth**

* `POST /auth/login` â€“ login with email/pass
* `POST /auth/register` â€“ create account
* `POST /auth/google` â€“ Google OAuth login

**Profile & Goals**

* `GET /profile` â€“ fetch user profile
* `PUT /profile` â€“ update profile (goals, boss type, preferences)
* `POST /goals` â€“ create a goal
* `GET /goals` â€“ list goals
* `GET /goals/:id` â€“ get goal details
* `PUT /goals/:id` â€“ update goal
* `DELETE /goals/:id` â€“ delete goal

**Tasks**

* `POST /tasks` â€“ create task (manual or AI suggested)
* `GET /tasks` â€“ list all tasks (filter: goal, status)
* `PUT /tasks/:id` â€“ update task (mark complete, edit)
* `DELETE /tasks/:id` â€“ delete task

**Journal**

* `POST /journal` â€“ create entry (morning/evening)
* `GET /journal` â€“ fetch entries (filter by date/type)
* `POST /journal/:id/analyze` â€“ AI analysis of journal

**Notifications**

* `GET /notifications` â€“ list history
* `POST /notifications/send` â€“ trigger push (test/dev)

**Team / Collaboration**

* `POST /team` â€“ add member
* `GET /team` â€“ list members
* `PUT /team/:id` â€“ update member
* `DELETE /team/:id` â€“ remove member

**AI Coach**

* `POST /ai/next-step` â€“ suggest next task from goal & thesis
* `POST /ai/review-day` â€“ analyze todayâ€™s journal & tasks
* `POST /ai/chat` â€“ boss-style communication (serious/funny/minion voice)

